name: Sweet Dreams
description:
Something that is difficult to express, maybe silly to understand. But this is real this is my dream.
Dream to travel the world. Visiting Korea, my dream place, France and many others. I even dreamed that I could see millions of billions of stars in the sky, meteors, meteors running in the sky and also the amazing planets I saw in my book. Sometimes I'm embarrassed to say it because someone will laugh at what I dream of.
oh my sweet dream
